data.title: Caetlyn Watson - Trivia, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Caetlyn Watson: her birthday, what she did before fame, her family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

Australian choreographer, dancer, entertainer, artist, and performer who has worked with artists like Janet Jackson and Kylie Minogue. She has been a dance instructor in many countries across the globe. Some of these countries have included Switzerland, Japan, and Mexico.

Before Fame

She began posting to her caetlynwatson Instagram account in October of 2016. One of her first posts is a picture of her wearing a black leather jacket.

Trivia

She enjoys spending time at the beach. In December of 2019, she directed a dance video dedicated to FKA Twigs. She has many tattoos all over body including on her back and arms.

Family Life

She was born in Australia. She is based in the region of Brisbane.
